Thank you everyone for being part of this incredible journey. We're deeply humbled and delighted to receive this award, recognizing our hard work. 
I, Devansh used to wake up at 6 am to shoot and create content for the whole week and help my dad in the family business and Maggi was an interior designer at a firm in Delhi, used to shoot early morning at weekends to keep up with the schedule. After getting married both of us took a leap of faith and left our previous roles to start our journey as content creators. 
And thanks to all of you for being a constant support and loving the content which motivates us to create more. 
.
Thank you @etimes @timesofindia @monikarawal99 for recognising our work and our amazing team at @cloutpocketaces @priyanshug0el @jahanvi_walia for making this happen. 
.
.
